      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VANZANT HAYZE (8) recorded a 4 length win in a Mix 5 last time 23.80 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. In form and rates on top again. FARMOR ROGUE (4) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing second (24.41) and beaten 0.8 lengths over 407m at this track. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Expected to feature again. SLICK RAM (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (24.57) in a Mix 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. EARLY SUPPER (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
